            "text": "<p>At 10 mg lutein + 2 mg zeaxanthin, these carotenoids improve word learning in older adults and enhance attention, memory, and reasoning in younger adults. Lutein accumulates in the hippocampus and frontal cortex -- key brain regions for learning.</p>"
