            "text": "<p>These carotenoids increase brain-derived neurotrophic factor (BDNF) -- a protein critical for learning, memory, and the growth of new neurons. <a href=\"/pages/lithium\" target=\"_blank\">Lithium</a> also increases BDNF through a different pathway.</p>"
